* 🔡 Text Generation and Summarization
* 🖼️ Text-to-Image with Diffusion Models
* 🧠 Embedding + Vector Similarity Search
* 🧮 Digit Recognition with CNNs
* 💬 LLM Prompt Engineering
* 🤗 Hugging Face Transformers and Pipelines
* 🧰 Tools: Google Colab, Python, OpenAI, Weaviate, TensorFlow, Matplotlib

