## 🧪 Sample Results

| Task               | Example Result                                                                              |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Text Summarization | `"A long story..." → "Summary in 2-3 lines"`                                                |
| Image Generation   | `"A panda riding a bicycle"` → 🐼 🚴‍♂️                                                     |
| GPT Completion     | `"Tell me a joke"` → `"Why don’t scientists trust atoms? Because they make up everything!"` |
| Digit Prediction   | Input: handwritten '5' → Predicted: `5`                                                     |
| Semantic Search    | Query: `"AI in healthcare"` → Returns top 5 matching docs                                   |

